At least 75 people are killed and over 200 injured in a wave of bombings in Shi'ite neighbourhoods across Baghdad as sectarian violence in Iraq continues to increase. (Reuters via News24)At least 27 people are killed in an al-Qaeda raid on the town of Seyoun in Hadramout province. (Reuters via Trust)Five British ISAF personnel are killed in a military helicopter crash in Kandahar province in southern Afghanistan. (BBC)